entry.string: Es gelten Zugriffsbeschränkungen. Access restrictions apply. In order to obtain the rights of use please contact the Central Office for Geotopography of the AdV (ZSGT) / Service Centre (DLZ) of the Federal Agency for Cartography and Geodesy: https://www.bkg.bund.de/DE/Service/Kontakt/kontakt.html.
